query:
select ts, mgmt_addr, meta_uuid, meta_event_name, meta_mgmturl, events_enrichment_target_process_node_key_value, sha1
                            from hive_datalake.views.dv_events_table_mgmts
                            where sha1 in ('426dc93fa10d28ca6b93f851300026c0f58128c5') and
                            ts >= '2021-10-14' and 
                            mgmt_addr = 'fao.sentinelone.net'
                            limit 1000
